snippet.title: Organ Quarter VR Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Releasing 19 October, 2017 for HTC Vive and Oculus Rift.
http://store.steampowered.com/app/605830/Organ_Quarter/

Organ Quarter is a survival horror VR game which takes place in an abandoned, nightmarish and surreal urban environment. Immerse yourself in the overwhelming dread of the Organ Quarter: large sprawling environments, gun combat, strict resource management and engaging puzzles.
